1
00:00:17,940 --> 00:00:21,260
♪The falling snow♪

2
00:00:21,620 --> 00:00:25,180
♪Is bitter cold♪

3
00:00:27,300 --> 00:00:29,980
♪My sigh♪

4
00:00:30,420 --> 00:00:34,460
♪Misted the path in front of me♪

5
00:00:36,620 --> 00:00:42,740
♪The moonlight knows my intention♪

6
00:00:44,860 --> 00:00:51,300
♪I just want to make
a place for me in your heart♪

7
00:00:53,820 --> 00:00:57,620
♪I laugh and I cry♪

8
00:00:58,340 --> 00:01:02,100
♪Quietly building a pond in my heart♪

9
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:06,780
♪I accept all the gifts from sorrow♪

10
00:01:07,580 --> 00:01:11,420
♪I can't let down my regrets♪

11
00:01:12,060 --> 00:01:15,860
♪I won't admit defeat♪

12
00:01:16,460 --> 00:01:20,260
♪I slowly chew
on the bitterness of life♪

13
00:01:20,980 --> 00:01:24,540
♪The fragrance remains
the same after the bleak winter♪

14
00:01:25,340 --> 00:01:29,540
♪Awaiting spring
to color the way back home♪

15
00:01:31,020 --> 00:01:36,340
[The Double]

16
00:01:36,340 --> 00:01:39,020
[Episode 26]

17
00:01:39,310 --> 00:01:40,720
The ghost fire was set by someone,

18
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:44,110
and those who were burned
must have been manipulated.

19
00:01:45,360 --> 00:01:46,960
Otherwise, they wouldn't
have said the same thing.

20
00:01:47,270 --> 00:01:50,080
Investigate all the victims'
whereabouts before they died

21
00:01:50,190 --> 00:01:51,360
to find anything that can link them.

22
00:01:51,910 --> 00:01:52,390
Yes, My Lord.

23
00:01:53,310 --> 00:01:54,880
The ghost fire is a cover.

24
00:01:55,830 --> 00:01:58,520
The real plot comes next.

25
00:02:01,190 --> 00:02:02,470
Any news from the Jiang family?

26
00:02:02,470 --> 00:02:04,240
Tomorrow is the Jiang family's
ancestor worship day.

27
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:05,640
There's not much besides that.

28
00:02:05,830 --> 00:02:07,910
Are you worried

29
00:02:07,910 --> 00:02:08,960
about Second Lady Jiang
being implicated?

30
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:10,800
Should I go and follow her?

31
00:02:11,270 --> 00:02:11,800
Come back here.

32
00:02:13,480 --> 00:02:14,320
Did I tell you to go?

33
00:02:14,870 --> 00:02:16,320
Focus on the main task.

34
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:23,360
Why is His Lordship so indecisive?

35
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:24,760
One moment,
he asked me to deliver a message

36
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:26,270
and stop me from following the next.

37
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:27,870
The last time you delivered the message,

38
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:29,590
Second Lady Jiang
didn't come to thank him.

39
00:02:30,550 --> 00:02:32,040
Of course, His Lordship is not happy.

40
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:34,800
That's not right.

41
00:02:35,110 --> 00:02:36,830
Why do you seem
to understand everything suddenly?

42
00:02:37,550 --> 00:02:38,920
I've always been like this.

43
00:02:40,040 --> 00:02:40,710
As for you,

44
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:44,040
Maybe you've turned into a fool
after being punished too many times.

45
00:02:49,620 --> 00:02:54,820
[Virtue Shines Through Time]

46
00:02:54,830 --> 00:02:58,800
Ancestors of the Jiang family,
bless our family,

47
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:03,830
[In Memory Jiang Chengye]
throughout the year continuously.

48
00:03:22,460 --> 00:03:26,060
[Virtue Shines Through Time]

49
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:37,390
Li.

50
00:03:41,830 --> 00:03:42,390
Jiang Li.

51
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,670
Where is her manner?

52
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:48,110
Yuanbai, this is against the rules.

53
00:03:56,060 --> 00:03:59,360
[In Memory of Ye Zhenzhen]

54
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,110
Madam Ye,

55
00:04:00,990 --> 00:04:02,990
you must be reunited with Jiang Li.

56
00:04:04,870 --> 00:04:05,920
Don't worry.

57
00:04:07,150 --> 00:04:08,430
I'm indebted to her,

58
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:10,960
so I will help her get justice.

59
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:12,800
Li,

60
00:04:13,150 --> 00:04:14,990
women can't join the worship.

61
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:18,200
You're breaking the rules.
Get down here.

62
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:19,200
That's right.

63
00:04:19,910 --> 00:04:20,520
My dear,

64
00:04:20,830 --> 00:04:23,790
it's my fault for not telling her.

65
00:04:24,830 --> 00:04:25,390
Father,

66
00:04:27,520 --> 00:04:29,000
I haven't seen mother for a long time.

67
00:04:30,270 --> 00:04:32,560
Please forgive me for being rude.

68
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:33,150
Li,

69
00:04:33,710 --> 00:04:35,640
didn't you hear the elders?

70
00:04:36,440 --> 00:04:39,120
It's one thing to act out at home.

71
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:42,960
But now you are in front
of the whole family and ancestors,

72
00:04:43,350 --> 00:04:44,760
so control yourself.

73
00:04:45,080 --> 00:04:46,520
I just want to bow to my mother.

74
00:04:48,230 --> 00:04:49,440
Please allow it, Mother.

75
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:51,320
It seems

76
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:53,470
you are determined
to break the rules today.

77
00:04:53,710 --> 00:04:55,200
I just want to pay my respects.

78
00:04:59,350 --> 00:05:00,030
Jiang Li.

79
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:02,030
Never mind.

80
00:05:03,270 --> 00:05:05,440
Let her worship this once.

81
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:08,230
These are rules set by our ancestors.

82
00:05:08,960 --> 00:05:10,200
Breaking them

83
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:12,590
will bring trouble to the family.

84
00:05:12,830 --> 00:05:13,470
My dear,

85
00:05:13,910 --> 00:05:15,230
someone has to teach her the rules.

86
00:05:15,640 --> 00:05:16,760
If none of you want
to be the bad person,

87
00:05:17,350 --> 00:05:18,120
I will do it.

88
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:21,830
My dear.

89
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:26,030
Jiang Li, get up.

90
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:27,520
Get up.

91
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:30,470
Get up.

92
00:05:30,830 --> 00:05:32,230
Where are your manners?

93
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,270
Get up.

94
00:05:34,880 --> 00:05:35,520
Get up.

95
00:05:36,200 --> 00:05:36,910
Stop bowing.

96
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:37,760
Let me go.

97
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:38,960
Get up.

98
00:05:39,520 --> 00:05:40,760
[Virtue Shines Through Time]
Don't disturb my Yue!

99
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:42,520
Don't disturb my Yue!

100
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:43,880
Don't bother my Yue!

101
00:05:44,350 --> 00:05:46,560
Get out! Get out!

102
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,350
How did she get out?

103
00:05:57,590 --> 00:05:58,120
Someone!

104
00:05:58,680 --> 00:05:59,680
Take her back!

105
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:02,030
- My Yue...
- Quickly!

106
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:04,390
- My dear Yue...
- Send her back!

107
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:07,320
My dear Yue.

108
00:06:07,590 --> 00:06:08,760
Yue, my dear Yue.

109
00:06:08,760 --> 00:06:10,080
- Come!
- Move it.

110
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:11,030
My dear Yue.

111
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:12,120
My dear Yue.

112
00:06:14,030 --> 00:06:16,230
Yue, my darling.

113
00:06:18,590 --> 00:06:19,440
[Aunt Hu]
Yue...

114
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:26,030
Madam, are you all right?

115
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:28,710
Let's go.

116
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:37,710
Let's go home.

117
00:06:37,860 --> 00:06:39,880
[Virtue Shines Through Time]

118
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:40,710
What a mess.

119
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:51,590
Jiang Li, you are so brave.

120
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:53,680
Actually, I also think

121
00:06:54,270 --> 00:06:56,440
it's unfair that women can't worship?

122
00:06:57,440 --> 00:06:58,590
Who was that woman?

123
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,320
That's Aunt Hu.

124
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:01,320
Don't you remember?

125
00:07:01,470 --> 00:07:02,270
When you were young,

126
00:07:02,390 --> 00:07:04,470
you were very close to Jiang Yue.

127
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:05,760
That is her daughter.

128
00:07:06,910 --> 00:07:07,790
Old Madam,

129
00:07:08,520 --> 00:07:10,150
please spare this child.

130
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:11,760
Please.

131
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:13,680
Aunt Hu was originally a maid
in the side court.

132
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:16,120
But she got pregnant before your mother,
who was the legal wife.

133
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:17,320
Because it's not accepted
within the societal norms,

134
00:07:18,030 --> 00:07:19,910
Grandmother didn't allow her
to keep the child.

135
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,470
After all, if she gave birth to a son,

136
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:24,350
the eldest son of the Jiang family
would be born to a maid,

137
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:25,390
which was quite embarrassing.

138
00:07:26,350 --> 00:07:27,230
However, your mother was kind-hearted.

139
00:07:27,790 --> 00:07:30,150
So she saved both Aunt Hu
and her unborn child.

140
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:32,520
For the sake of the child,

141
00:07:33,270 --> 00:07:34,200
please spare her.

142
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:41,880
Aunt Hu was grateful
for your mother's kindness.

143
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:44,150
She never competed or caused trouble
and was kind to everyone.

144
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:47,120
About two years later,
your mother had you.

145
00:07:48,230 --> 00:07:49,830
The harmony among the wives
and concubines of the Jiang family

146
00:07:50,030 --> 00:07:52,560
became a good story
among the upper-class households.

147
00:07:54,830 --> 00:07:55,640
What happened after that?

148
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,470
Everything changed

149
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:01,120
after your mother's death.

150
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:25,390
Jiang Yue accidentally drowned
while playing near the artificial hill.

151
00:08:25,900 --> 00:08:26,490
It took hours

152
00:08:26,730 --> 00:08:28,930
before a passing servant girl
found her body.

153
00:08:30,850 --> 00:08:32,890
- Someone died!
- Help!

154
00:08:32,890 --> 00:08:33,730
Yue, get up.

155
00:08:34,460 --> 00:08:36,370
Wake up. Open your eyes and look at me.

156
00:08:36,940 --> 00:08:38,940
Look at me.
I'll take you home, all right?

157
00:08:40,010 --> 00:08:42,940
I'll take you home. Yue!

158
00:08:45,370 --> 00:08:46,130
Yue!

159
00:08:46,130 --> 00:08:48,370
From then on, Aunt Hu
was heartbroken day and night,

160
00:08:48,770 --> 00:08:49,610
eventually developing hysteria.

161
00:08:50,460 --> 00:08:52,650
She wandered around
the house looking disheveled.

162
00:08:53,420 --> 00:08:54,610
There was no other choice

163
00:08:54,850 --> 00:08:56,770
but to lock her in the woodshed
in the backyard.

164
00:08:57,340 --> 00:08:58,460
Yue!

165
00:08:59,250 --> 00:09:01,370
But if she's locked in the woodshed,

166
00:09:01,820 --> 00:09:03,010
how did she end up here?

167
00:09:03,460 --> 00:09:04,420
That is why it's strange.

168
00:09:05,100 --> 00:09:06,940
When you were sent to Zhennyu Hall,

169
00:09:07,250 --> 00:09:09,300
Aunt Hu disappeared from the woodshed.

170
00:09:09,850 --> 00:09:11,220
Ji Shuran searched for her
for a long time,

171
00:09:11,220 --> 00:09:12,340
but couldn't find her.

172
00:09:12,490 --> 00:09:14,300
Aunt Hu! Aunt Hu!

173
00:09:14,940 --> 00:09:16,460
Later, guess where she went?

174
00:09:19,850 --> 00:09:22,100
She's a madwoman with no carriage.

175
00:09:22,610 --> 00:09:24,730
No one knows how she got here.

176
00:09:25,220 --> 00:09:26,940
But according to Grandmother,

177
00:09:27,180 --> 00:09:31,060
she always warned not
to bring trouble to the Jiang family.

178
00:09:31,060 --> 00:09:32,010
Grandmother thought

179
00:09:32,010 --> 00:09:34,060
it was risky to keep her at home.

180
00:09:34,460 --> 00:09:35,980
So she ordered someone

181
00:09:36,300 --> 00:09:37,610
to tidy up this room

182
00:09:37,610 --> 00:09:38,770
and consider her guarding the tomb.

183
00:09:38,940 --> 00:09:41,610
It seems Aunt Hu is also a pitiful soul.

184
00:09:42,300 --> 00:09:44,060
Since she was so close to my mother,

185
00:09:44,610 --> 00:09:47,250
I should visit her often in the future.

186
00:09:47,370 --> 00:09:48,180
You can't.

187
00:09:48,610 --> 00:09:50,650
She's mad and can be violent.

188
00:09:50,770 --> 00:09:51,770
Moreover, if you keep coming,

189
00:09:52,060 --> 00:09:53,180
what if others see her?

190
00:09:53,580 --> 00:09:54,580
They'll start gossiping.

191
00:09:54,700 --> 00:09:56,980
Never mind. There will be opportunities
to visit her in the future.

192
00:09:58,980 --> 00:09:59,610
All right.

193
00:10:02,890 --> 00:10:03,460
Tong,

194
00:10:04,850 --> 00:10:06,460
do you find Aunt Hu

195
00:10:06,460 --> 00:10:07,130
a little strange?

196
00:10:07,940 --> 00:10:09,890
Strange? How so?

197
00:10:10,250 --> 00:10:12,530
Just now, she seemed
to be observing me secretly.

198
00:10:12,980 --> 00:10:14,820
Especially after I confronted Ji Shuran,

199
00:10:14,980 --> 00:10:16,610
her gaze was fixed on me.

200
00:10:17,130 --> 00:10:18,220
It's just strange.

201
00:10:18,580 --> 00:10:20,650
Are you suspecting
that she's not really hysterical?

202
00:10:21,180 --> 00:10:24,250
But how could
an ordinary person pretend to be crazy

203
00:10:24,580 --> 00:10:26,060
and guard a dead person's tomb?

204
00:10:28,220 --> 00:10:29,900
[Jiang Family Ancestral Temple]

205
00:10:31,060 --> 00:10:31,700
Let's go.

206
00:11:03,490 --> 00:11:04,460
Are you all right?

207
00:11:05,420 --> 00:11:06,130
I'm fine.

208
00:11:10,980 --> 00:11:11,820
What's going on?

209
00:11:12,770 --> 00:11:14,490
Second Lady, I'm really sorry.

210
00:11:14,850 --> 00:11:16,180
The reins unexpectedly broke.

211
00:11:16,340 --> 00:11:17,340
The horse also ran off.

212
00:11:17,770 --> 00:11:18,650
Why does

213
00:11:18,650 --> 00:11:20,100
the rein suddenly break for no reason?

214
00:11:20,300 --> 00:11:21,100
Maybe it's worn out.

215
00:11:21,580 --> 00:11:22,730
I'll go and find the horse right away.

216
00:11:22,890 --> 00:11:23,580
Hurry.

217
00:11:34,300 --> 00:11:35,300
What happened to you?

218
00:11:35,610 --> 00:11:37,530
Ruoyao, my horse ran away.

219
00:11:38,460 --> 00:11:39,490
What luck.

220
00:11:40,100 --> 00:11:42,460
Jinhua, stay with her maid here.

221
00:11:42,890 --> 00:11:43,890
You can ride in my carriage
and leave first.

222
00:11:44,340 --> 00:11:44,820
Yes.

223
00:11:47,340 --> 00:11:49,370
Why? Are you planning to go back later

224
00:11:49,700 --> 00:11:51,180
and play the victim in front

225
00:11:51,180 --> 00:11:52,250
of Father and Grandmother?

226
00:11:52,730 --> 00:11:54,460
You're always good at spinning tales.

227
00:11:54,770 --> 00:11:56,060
I don't want to go back

228
00:11:56,420 --> 00:11:57,340
and have you accuse

229
00:11:57,340 --> 00:11:59,130
my mother of damaging your carriage
and plotting against you again.

230
00:12:06,490 --> 00:12:09,100
In that case, thank you for the ride.

231
00:12:17,300 --> 00:12:18,250
You should know

232
00:12:18,490 --> 00:12:20,060
about my marriage with the Qi family.

233
00:12:20,770 --> 00:12:21,460
I heard.

234
00:12:21,770 --> 00:12:23,890
You ruined my engagement
with Zhou Yanbang.

235
00:12:24,420 --> 00:12:26,340
You must be happy now.

236
00:12:26,530 --> 00:12:28,010
He is not a good husband prospect
for you.

237
00:12:28,250 --> 00:12:29,060
You know nothing.

238
00:12:29,730 --> 00:12:30,610
The matter has come to this.

239
00:12:31,300 --> 00:12:33,060
Do you feel remorse?

240
00:12:35,530 --> 00:12:36,940
If I'm not mistaken,

241
00:12:37,650 --> 00:12:41,100
it was you and Ji Shuran
who tried to set me up first.

242
00:12:41,370 --> 00:12:42,770
That's because you've been targeting us

243
00:12:42,890 --> 00:12:44,250
since you returned.

244
00:12:44,420 --> 00:12:45,250
If you

245
00:12:45,340 --> 00:12:47,010
had stayed quietly at Zhennyu Hall,

246
00:12:47,700 --> 00:12:49,650
none of this would have happened to me.

247
00:12:49,940 --> 00:12:51,420
I'll still be the Jiang's family's
only legitimate daughter.

248
00:12:51,580 --> 00:12:54,340
It's all your fault.
It's all because of you.

249
00:12:54,940 --> 00:12:56,890
You say I've taken everything from you.

250
00:12:58,460 --> 00:12:59,580
But have you ever thought

251
00:13:00,250 --> 00:13:01,610
about where did you get it from

252
00:13:01,940 --> 00:13:03,460
and from whom did you get it from?

253
00:13:03,770 --> 00:13:04,420
Do you know

254
00:13:04,770 --> 00:13:06,730
what kind of life I had at Zhennyu Hall?

255
00:13:08,890 --> 00:13:11,460
What concern is it of mine
how you lived at Zhennyu Hall?

256
00:13:12,340 --> 00:13:13,010
Give me your hand.

257
00:13:17,370 --> 00:13:17,890
Does it hurt?

258
00:13:18,820 --> 00:13:19,770
I'm asking you if it hurts.

259
00:13:21,730 --> 00:13:23,650
The pain I endured at Zhennyu Hall

260
00:13:23,650 --> 00:13:25,770
was a thousand times worse than this.

261
00:13:26,580 --> 00:13:27,580
When I was eight,

262
00:13:27,980 --> 00:13:30,100
did I really cause harm to your mother?

263
00:13:31,610 --> 00:13:32,340
They framed me

264
00:13:32,730 --> 00:13:34,250
and sent me to Zhennyu Hall unjustly.

265
00:13:35,370 --> 00:13:35,770
Why?

266
00:13:36,530 --> 00:13:38,650
Can't I return to clear my name?

267
00:13:40,530 --> 00:13:42,530
I have no bias

268
00:13:42,980 --> 00:13:43,770
or grudges against you.

269
00:13:45,650 --> 00:13:46,940
We were both young back then.

270
00:13:48,010 --> 00:13:50,340
I believe it wasn't your idea

271
00:13:50,340 --> 00:13:52,130
for me to stay
at Zhennyu Hall for so long.

272
00:13:52,460 --> 00:13:53,370
Now that I'm back,

273
00:13:53,980 --> 00:13:55,220
I just want to reclaim

274
00:13:55,460 --> 00:13:57,220
what rightfully belongs to Jiang Li,

275
00:13:57,490 --> 00:13:58,250
nothing more.

276
00:13:59,130 --> 00:14:00,300
If you insist

277
00:14:00,420 --> 00:14:02,340
that I took everything from you

278
00:14:02,340 --> 00:14:03,650
and keep pressuring me,

279
00:14:04,820 --> 00:14:07,370
I can only tell you one thing.
You're a fool.

280
00:14:07,490 --> 00:14:09,420
What did you say? Say it again.

281
00:14:09,420 --> 00:14:10,490
What's there to be afraid of?

282
00:14:10,580 --> 00:14:10,820
I...

283
00:14:10,980 --> 00:14:11,650
Jiang Ruoyao,

284
00:14:11,890 --> 00:14:13,890
have you gone mad
from staying at the mansion?

285
00:14:14,490 --> 00:14:16,180
As the legitimate daughter
of the Jiang family,

286
00:14:16,490 --> 00:14:17,890
you've shattered our sisterly bond

287
00:14:18,300 --> 00:14:19,770
for such a worthless person
from the Zhou family.

288
00:14:19,940 --> 00:14:21,370
Think carefully about it.

289
00:14:22,220 --> 00:14:23,010
Do you not regret it?

290
00:14:23,980 --> 00:14:25,060
Now that I call you foolish,

291
00:14:25,490 --> 00:14:26,700
that's the least of it.

292
00:14:27,010 --> 00:14:29,610
Do you think I would listen to you

293
00:14:29,700 --> 00:14:30,650
after talking big in front of me?

294
00:14:30,940 --> 00:14:31,580
No matter what,

295
00:14:31,890 --> 00:14:33,060
you owe me.

296
00:14:33,940 --> 00:14:36,420
You must pay
for what you've done to me.

297
00:14:37,100 --> 00:14:37,820
What price?

298
00:14:48,820 --> 00:14:51,610
Don't move. Behave and come with me.

299
00:15:59,460 --> 00:16:00,650
Why did you knock her out?

300
00:16:01,180 --> 00:16:03,220
Didn't you say
we were only after money?

301
00:16:03,580 --> 00:16:05,730
You could've asked her
about the money and left.

302
00:16:05,940 --> 00:16:06,770
By delaying like this,

303
00:16:06,980 --> 00:16:07,220
what if we get caught...

304
00:16:07,220 --> 00:16:08,890
She's the obstacle between us.

305
00:16:09,650 --> 00:16:10,100
Without her,

306
00:16:10,100 --> 00:16:11,370
we could have been together long ago.

307
00:16:12,220 --> 00:16:12,850
Think about it.

308
00:16:12,980 --> 00:16:14,130
Before Jiang Li came back,

309
00:16:14,300 --> 00:16:15,730
you were the most beautiful lady
in the city,

310
00:16:15,730 --> 00:16:17,130
with excellent musical talent.

311
00:16:17,460 --> 00:16:19,530
I was also a handsome
and talented young man.

312
00:16:20,650 --> 00:16:22,060
We've become like this now.

313
00:16:22,730 --> 00:16:24,460
Shouldn't Jiang Li die?

314
00:16:24,460 --> 00:16:25,250
Shouldn't she?

315
00:16:25,980 --> 00:16:27,220
Are you planning to kill her?

316
00:16:27,370 --> 00:16:28,530
In the deep mountains and forests,

317
00:16:28,940 --> 00:16:31,130
who would know we were behind this?

318
00:16:32,010 --> 00:16:34,890
Even if we were caught,
family secrets must not be revealed.

319
00:16:35,370 --> 00:16:36,650
The Jiang family and the Zhou family

320
00:16:36,650 --> 00:16:37,820
will protect us at all costs.

321
00:16:37,890 --> 00:16:38,850
Are you crazy?

322
00:16:39,340 --> 00:16:40,250
This is a human life!

323
00:16:40,250 --> 00:16:41,650
She's always been a troublemaker.

324
00:16:41,700 --> 00:16:42,890
We won't have peace until she's gone!

325
00:16:43,940 --> 00:16:44,530
Ruoyao,

326
00:16:45,180 --> 00:16:45,850
I'm doing this

327
00:16:46,060 --> 00:16:47,610
so we can be together.

328
00:16:48,010 --> 00:16:48,770
Last night,

329
00:16:49,980 --> 00:16:50,890
have you forgotten

330
00:16:52,300 --> 00:16:53,340
what you said?

331
00:16:54,300 --> 00:16:54,940
Ruoyao,

332
00:16:56,490 --> 00:16:58,100
I finally get to see you.

333
00:16:59,650 --> 00:17:02,100
Aren't you already married to Yu'e?

334
00:17:02,340 --> 00:17:04,570
Why are you saying these things now?

335
00:17:04,700 --> 00:17:07,330
Ruoyao, you knew

336
00:17:07,730 --> 00:17:09,010
I was set up.

337
00:17:09,730 --> 00:17:10,530
Besides,

338
00:17:10,530 --> 00:17:12,010
I've never stopped sending you letters
all this time.

339
00:17:13,010 --> 00:17:14,490
I've never touched Jiang Yu'e.

340
00:17:14,530 --> 00:17:15,730
You're the only one in my heart.

341
00:17:15,730 --> 00:17:17,380
What's the use of saying all this now?

342
00:17:17,620 --> 00:17:18,250
Do you know...

343
00:17:21,180 --> 00:17:21,900
Do you know

344
00:17:22,570 --> 00:17:25,010
my mother wants to marry me off
to the Qi family?

345
00:17:26,330 --> 00:17:27,050
How

346
00:17:29,050 --> 00:17:29,980
about we elope?

347
00:17:33,090 --> 00:17:33,900
What?

348
00:17:36,010 --> 00:17:37,490
Let's elope to another place.

349
00:17:38,860 --> 00:17:41,180
To a place surrounded
by green hills and clear waters.

350
00:17:41,730 --> 00:17:42,700
We'll gather some money

351
00:17:43,460 --> 00:17:45,010
and live a simple life there,

352
00:17:45,290 --> 00:17:46,010
away from Yan Capital,

353
00:17:46,010 --> 00:17:47,730
away from everyone
and everything you dislike.

354
00:17:48,010 --> 00:17:49,050
Just us.

355
00:17:50,730 --> 00:17:53,980
But my mother is keeping
a close eye on me now.

356
00:17:54,620 --> 00:17:55,660
I'm afraid

357
00:17:56,090 --> 00:17:57,980
it'll be hard to get money from home.

358
00:17:58,570 --> 00:17:59,900
I can't bear to see you suffer.

359
00:18:00,530 --> 00:18:01,730
I'll gather the money myself.

360
00:18:02,220 --> 00:18:04,620
If necessary, I can work as a laborer.

361
00:18:05,090 --> 00:18:07,010
In any case, I won't let you suffer.

362
00:18:07,380 --> 00:18:09,570
You're from a prestigious family,
a scholarly family.

363
00:18:09,900 --> 00:18:11,010
- How can you...
- So what?

364
00:18:11,770 --> 00:18:13,090
I just want to be with you.

365
00:18:15,660 --> 00:18:16,290
Ruoyao,

366
00:18:17,220 --> 00:18:18,460
I suddenly remembered someone.

367
00:18:19,860 --> 00:18:21,250
She should provide the money.

368
00:18:24,730 --> 00:18:25,420
Who?

369
00:18:25,810 --> 00:18:26,530
Jiang Li.

370
00:18:26,980 --> 00:18:28,570
She has the backing
of the wealthy Ye family.

371
00:18:28,940 --> 00:18:30,140
If we capture her,

372
00:18:30,490 --> 00:18:31,860
we can get a lot of money.

373
00:18:32,900 --> 00:18:34,620
It'll be enough for our future.

374
00:18:37,530 --> 00:18:40,220
You've wanted
to kill her from the start.

375
00:18:41,220 --> 00:18:41,810
Am I right?

376
00:18:42,460 --> 00:18:43,730
You've been lying to me all along.

377
00:18:43,810 --> 00:18:45,980
Ruoyao, trust me.

378
00:18:46,290 --> 00:18:47,460
I won't harm you.

379
00:18:47,860 --> 00:18:49,530
Ruoyao, believe me.

380
00:18:49,810 --> 00:18:50,420
Ruoyao.

381
00:18:50,620 --> 00:18:51,420
Ruoyao, you can't leave.

382
00:18:51,490 --> 00:18:52,860
If you leave, it'll be over for us!

383
00:18:52,980 --> 00:18:53,570
Let me go.

384
00:18:53,570 --> 00:18:54,660
- Ruoyao, listen to me.
- Let me go!

385
00:18:54,940 --> 00:18:55,810
Ruoyao! Ruoyao!

386
00:19:06,460 --> 00:19:08,220
Why are all of you forcing me?

387
00:19:09,180 --> 00:19:13,980
Jiang Li must pay the price.

388
00:19:28,700 --> 00:19:30,380
On the day of the palace banquet,
I asked to see you.

389
00:19:31,770 --> 00:19:32,940
It would've been fine
if you didn't come.

390
00:19:34,460 --> 00:19:36,140
Why did you have to set me up?

391
00:19:36,380 --> 00:19:37,980
I never intended to set you up.

392
00:19:39,700 --> 00:19:41,860
That day, I was just like you.

393
00:19:42,730 --> 00:19:44,380
I was also a victim of the trap.

394
00:19:46,620 --> 00:19:47,730
Stop deceiving me.

395
00:19:47,730 --> 00:19:49,010
Jiang Yu'e has told me everything.

396
00:19:49,010 --> 00:19:50,250
It was you who's been scheming
behind my back.

397
00:19:50,770 --> 00:19:52,090
I don't understand what you're saying.

398
00:19:52,730 --> 00:19:54,380
It's you who betrayed me.

399
00:19:54,900 --> 00:19:59,090
It was you who caused me
to fall to this point.

400
00:19:59,770 --> 00:20:01,010
You can't escape.

401
00:20:06,180 --> 00:20:06,940
Jiang Li,

402
00:20:08,700 --> 00:20:10,660
you do think your status
is precious, right?

403
00:20:13,250 --> 00:20:13,980
Well,

404
00:20:15,620 --> 00:20:18,090
why don't we make up
for the previous night

405
00:20:18,530 --> 00:20:19,250
together?

406
00:20:23,900 --> 00:20:24,660
Zhou Yanbang,

407
00:20:25,940 --> 00:20:28,290
you're the son
of the Marquis of Ningyuan.

408
00:20:28,770 --> 00:20:30,380
How can your mind be so muddled?

409
00:20:30,730 --> 00:20:31,980
Can't you even figure out

410
00:20:31,980 --> 00:20:32,860
who's the one really harming you?

411
00:20:33,940 --> 00:20:35,140
Who do you think you are?

412
00:20:35,250 --> 00:20:36,660
Who are you to lecture me?

413
00:20:37,010 --> 00:20:40,010
If anything happens to me today,

414
00:20:41,700 --> 00:20:43,220
do you think you'll escape?

415
00:20:43,570 --> 00:20:45,140
Even if the Zhou family
and the Jiang family don't pursue it,

416
00:20:45,530 --> 00:20:46,660
I still have the Ye family behind me.

417
00:20:47,050 --> 00:20:49,220
If you, a hereditary nobleman
end up in jail,

418
00:20:49,770 --> 00:20:50,980
you'll ruin your reputation

419
00:20:51,220 --> 00:20:52,770
and disgrace the Zhou family.

420
00:20:59,330 --> 00:21:00,700
Oh, Jiang Li.

421
00:21:01,530 --> 00:21:02,980
I almost fell for your deception again.

422
00:21:04,330 --> 00:21:05,770
But you've reminded me of something.

423
00:21:06,810 --> 00:21:08,220
After I'm done with you,

424
00:21:09,940 --> 00:21:13,380
I'll cut your tendons, and your hands,

425
00:21:13,730 --> 00:21:15,900
and cut off your tongue.

426
00:21:16,140 --> 00:21:19,900
Finally, I'll gouge out your eyes.

427
00:21:20,460 --> 00:21:22,900
Then you won't be able to speak, write,

428
00:21:22,900 --> 00:21:24,220
or see.

429
00:21:24,620 --> 00:21:26,460
How will you accuse me then?

430
00:21:48,250 --> 00:21:48,860
Wait.

431
00:21:49,940 --> 00:21:50,570
Zhou Yanbang,

432
00:21:51,810 --> 00:21:53,380
are you not afraid
of breaking Ruoyao's heart

433
00:21:53,660 --> 00:21:55,090
for doing this to me?

434
00:21:55,810 --> 00:21:59,050
Among us Jiang sisters, we each have
our own desires and grievances,

435
00:21:59,620 --> 00:22:00,860
except Ruoyao alone.

436
00:22:01,250 --> 00:22:02,330
She desires nothing else.

437
00:22:02,900 --> 00:22:04,290
She only has you in her heart.

438
00:22:04,330 --> 00:22:05,700
No matter what I do,

439
00:22:06,250 --> 00:22:07,700
she'll forgive me

440
00:22:08,180 --> 00:22:09,660
as long as I coax her.

441
00:22:10,660 --> 00:22:13,250
She's been strictly controlled
by her mother since childhood.

442
00:22:13,490 --> 00:22:14,490
She lacks determination.

443
00:22:14,770 --> 00:22:16,180
She'll obediently follow me

444
00:22:17,730 --> 00:22:20,010
if I coax her a little.

445
00:22:20,330 --> 00:22:21,290
As for you,

446
00:22:22,290 --> 00:22:25,220
you're so independent like a wild horse,

447
00:22:26,220 --> 00:22:29,620
making people want to conquer you.

448
00:22:29,900 --> 00:22:30,530
Shameless.

449
00:22:30,940 --> 00:22:32,330
Ruoyao forgives you

450
00:22:33,010 --> 00:22:34,010
because she likes you.

451
00:22:34,860 --> 00:22:36,250
You're using her feelings.

452
00:22:36,980 --> 00:22:38,380
Do you really have her in your heart?

453
00:22:38,460 --> 00:22:40,530
If she wasn't Jiang Yuanbai's daughter,

454
00:22:41,330 --> 00:22:42,730
would I have been engaged to her?

455
00:22:45,010 --> 00:22:46,010
No more questions, right?

456
00:22:47,090 --> 00:22:48,140
Let's begin.

457
00:22:49,620 --> 00:22:50,330
Don't touch me!

458
00:22:51,380 --> 00:22:51,900
Get off me!

459
00:22:52,380 --> 00:22:52,980
Zhou Yanbang,

460
00:22:54,660 --> 00:22:57,140
you brought this upon yourself.

461
00:23:06,050 --> 00:23:06,900
I killed someone.

462
00:23:09,420 --> 00:23:10,290
I killed someone.

463
00:23:12,380 --> 00:23:13,290
I killed someone.

464
00:23:19,940 --> 00:23:21,220
I killed someone.

465
00:23:30,420 --> 00:23:31,050
Don't panic.

466
00:23:32,810 --> 00:23:33,530
He's not dead.

467
00:23:34,380 --> 00:23:34,940
Jiang Ruoyao,

468
00:23:35,810 --> 00:23:36,770
you've sacrificed so much

469
00:23:37,570 --> 00:23:39,730
for someone like him.

470
00:23:42,860 --> 00:23:43,490
Once you're done crying,

471
00:23:44,290 --> 00:23:45,490
we should hurry up and go home.

472
00:23:46,330 --> 00:23:48,010
This matter might not be easy to handle.

473
00:23:48,570 --> 00:23:49,250
Considering

474
00:23:49,250 --> 00:23:50,980
that you promptly knocked out
Zhou Yanbang in time,

475
00:23:52,090 --> 00:23:53,290
I'll let go

476
00:23:53,420 --> 00:23:54,770
of your role in bringing me here.

477
00:23:55,460 --> 00:23:56,620
You need to figure out

478
00:23:57,050 --> 00:23:58,290
how to explain this to the Zhou family.

479
00:24:34,940 --> 00:24:38,380
[Jiang's Residence]

480
00:24:42,700 --> 00:24:43,290
Madam.

481
00:24:45,220 --> 00:24:45,730
Madam.

482
00:24:46,220 --> 00:24:46,980
Has Ruoyao returned?

483
00:24:49,530 --> 00:24:50,860
Why hasn't she come back yet?

484
00:24:50,860 --> 00:24:51,810
Wasn't she supposed

485
00:24:51,810 --> 00:24:52,700
to return with our convoy?

486
00:24:52,900 --> 00:24:54,090
I find it strange too.

487
00:24:54,380 --> 00:24:55,460
Even Jiang Li

488
00:24:55,530 --> 00:24:56,570
hasn't returned.

489
00:24:56,620 --> 00:24:57,140
What?

490
00:24:57,420 --> 00:24:58,010
Madam Sun.

491
00:24:58,570 --> 00:24:59,090
Madam Sun.

492
00:25:04,700 --> 00:25:05,090
All right.

493
00:25:05,660 --> 00:25:06,140
What happened?

494
00:25:07,290 --> 00:25:09,050
She said Jiang Li
and the Third Lady returned together.

495
00:25:09,290 --> 00:25:10,330
But they were covered in blood.

496
00:25:10,660 --> 00:25:11,220
What?

497
00:25:15,530 --> 00:25:17,180
The daughter of the Grand Chancellor,

498
00:25:18,460 --> 00:25:20,940
making such a ridiculous mistake
of eloping with someone.

499
00:25:21,460 --> 00:25:22,490
Don't you care about your reputation?

500
00:25:22,940 --> 00:25:24,220
Don't you even know you were being used?

501
00:25:24,620 --> 00:25:26,860
How did I raise such a foolish daughter?

502
00:25:29,980 --> 00:25:31,530
Mother, what should I do?

503
00:25:31,900 --> 00:25:32,900
What should I do?

504
00:25:32,900 --> 00:25:34,420
Why didn't you think about the outcome
before causing trouble?

505
00:25:34,810 --> 00:25:37,180
I'm scared, Mother.

506
00:25:37,250 --> 00:25:38,220
You brought this upon yourself.

507
00:25:38,460 --> 00:25:39,140
Mother.

508
00:25:39,140 --> 00:25:39,770
Don't call me.

509
00:25:40,220 --> 00:25:41,090
From today on,

510
00:25:41,700 --> 00:25:43,010
stay in this courtyard.

511
00:25:43,570 --> 00:25:45,090
You're not allowed to leave
without my permission.

512
00:25:45,660 --> 00:25:46,770
Mother.

513
00:25:49,770 --> 00:25:50,420
Madam,

514
00:25:50,980 --> 00:25:52,900
the Third Lady is scared right now.

515
00:25:52,980 --> 00:25:54,020
She should be comforted.

516
00:25:54,020 --> 00:25:54,770
Comfort?

517
00:25:55,130 --> 00:25:57,130
She doesn't even think
about the foolish things she's done.

518
00:25:57,420 --> 00:25:58,610
I spoiled her too much in the past,

519
00:25:58,940 --> 00:26:00,370
which led to her being so reckless.

520
00:26:01,180 --> 00:26:02,810
Now, let her reflect on her actions.

521
00:26:05,530 --> 00:26:07,980
Go and pass a message to Jiang Yu'e.

522
00:26:08,290 --> 00:26:09,570
Remember, don't let anyone see you.

523
00:26:09,770 --> 00:26:10,530
Just say...

524
00:26:15,330 --> 00:26:15,850
Yes, Madam.

525
00:26:20,500 --> 00:26:23,740
Oh, my son. Yanbang.

526
00:26:25,810 --> 00:26:27,570
My poor son.

527
00:26:28,460 --> 00:26:31,330
What am I supposed to do now?

528
00:26:32,740 --> 00:26:33,900
I hurriedly went

529
00:26:34,610 --> 00:26:36,420
and saw Li's back figure leaving

530
00:26:37,090 --> 00:26:39,570
and my husband covered in blood,

531
00:26:39,810 --> 00:26:40,900
unconscious on the ground.

532
00:26:41,980 --> 00:26:44,980
My poor son.

533
00:26:46,180 --> 00:26:46,940
Jiang Li!

534
00:26:47,610 --> 00:26:48,660
Come out!

535
00:26:48,660 --> 00:26:49,180
You can go in.

536
00:26:49,180 --> 00:26:50,090
Why are you stopping me?

537
00:26:50,180 --> 00:26:51,180
Don't stop me!

538
00:26:51,260 --> 00:26:51,850
Get out of my way!

539
00:26:52,460 --> 00:26:53,530
- What are you doing?
- Grand Chancellor Jiang.

540
00:26:54,050 --> 00:26:55,050
Grand Chancellor Jiang!

541
00:26:55,330 --> 00:26:57,290
- My son is dying.
- Madam.

542
00:26:57,420 --> 00:26:58,900
It's because of Jiang Li.

543
00:26:59,220 --> 00:27:02,260
She must come out and explain today.

544
00:27:02,570 --> 00:27:03,370
Jiang Li!

545
00:27:03,370 --> 00:27:05,610
- Calm down, Madam.
- Jiang Li, come out here!

546
00:27:06,020 --> 00:27:08,460
Or else I won't leave today.

547
00:27:08,900 --> 00:27:11,130
Jiang Li, come out!

548
00:27:11,850 --> 00:27:13,330
Come out!

549
00:27:26,530 --> 00:27:27,500
Have you found Jiuyue?

550
00:27:27,770 --> 00:27:29,570
My Lord, it's not like you don't know.

551
00:27:29,570 --> 00:27:30,980
She's the one
who usually comes and finds us.

552
00:27:30,980 --> 00:27:32,370
When have we ever managed
to track her whereabouts?

553
00:27:32,740 --> 00:27:34,290
Why are you so anxious?

554
00:27:34,810 --> 00:27:36,330
Second Lady Jiang is in trouble.

555
00:27:48,810 --> 00:27:49,500
