So why did Jiang Li go out?

830
00:40:23,250 --> 00:40:24,050
No need to explain.

831
00:40:25,780 --> 00:40:26,690
I think I know.

832
00:40:47,650 --> 00:40:49,820
I remember the last time
you invited me to dinner

833
00:40:50,090 --> 00:40:51,980
it was in Luyang for some buns.

834
00:40:52,730 --> 00:40:54,050
This time, you're really generous.

835
00:40:54,980 --> 00:40:56,420
That day, you beat Tong Zhiyang.

836
00:40:56,980 --> 00:40:58,300
But you weren't happy.

837
00:41:00,090 --> 00:41:00,650
How about now?

838
00:41:03,530 --> 00:41:04,380
Can we have a drink to celebrate?

839
00:41:04,730 --> 00:41:06,090
Do you think I won this time?

840
00:41:06,730 --> 00:41:07,900
Winning or losing isn't important.

841
00:41:09,300 --> 00:41:11,420
But you can't skip the meal.

842
00:41:14,940 --> 00:41:16,170
Do you know

843
00:41:16,860 --> 00:41:18,500
every move that I make?

844
00:41:18,650 --> 00:41:19,650
A player always knows

845
00:41:20,570 --> 00:41:22,940
where their pieces are.

846
00:41:27,900 --> 00:41:29,860
Do we have a chance to switch roles?

847
00:41:32,530 --> 00:41:33,570
I'd like to play the game.

848
00:41:34,420 --> 00:41:36,130
I want to compete

849
00:41:36,250 --> 00:41:38,250
with those people in Capital of Yan.

850
00:41:38,610 --> 00:41:39,530
Using what pieces?

851
00:41:41,460 --> 00:41:42,020
Me?

852
00:41:44,570 --> 00:41:46,170
You can say that.

853
00:41:47,050 --> 00:41:47,690
But I dare not.

854
00:41:48,500 --> 00:41:49,530
But I do wonder

855
00:41:49,980 --> 00:41:51,610
if a woman like me

856
00:41:51,980 --> 00:41:54,090
could ever see a bigger world?

857
00:41:57,090 --> 00:41:57,690
Enough talk.

858
00:41:58,650 --> 00:42:00,050
I should thank you

859
00:42:00,050 --> 00:42:01,500
for today's feast.

860
00:42:01,860 --> 00:42:02,940
I am happy today.

861
00:42:03,650 --> 00:42:04,650
But I must say,

862
00:42:04,650 --> 00:42:05,780
I can't drink much.

863
00:42:05,980 --> 00:42:06,690
Just this one cup.

864
00:42:07,090 --> 00:42:08,690
If I offend you,

865
00:42:08,980 --> 00:42:10,650
please don't send me away.

866
00:42:10,940 --> 00:42:11,530
Well, I won't go that far.

867
00:42:12,980 --> 00:42:13,900
By the way,

868
00:42:14,250 --> 00:42:15,650
Situ Jiuyue is not in the capital.

869
00:42:16,050 --> 00:42:18,380
It might take some time to find her.

870
00:42:18,380 --> 00:42:20,730
I thank you on behalf of Magistrate Xue.

871
00:42:38,900 --> 00:42:40,090
Are you already drunk with just one cup?

872
00:42:40,730 --> 00:42:43,860
No, I'm just tired

873
00:42:44,540 --> 00:42:45,420
after the commotion this morning.

874
00:42:46,570 --> 00:42:47,530
I'd like to take a nap.

875
00:42:48,050 --> 00:42:48,860
Then sleep.

876
00:44:04,380 --> 00:44:05,820
Everywhere else is not comfortable.

877
00:44:07,690 --> 00:44:09,500
But the place you picked

878
00:44:11,130 --> 00:44:12,050
sure is not bad.

879
00:44:13,570 --> 00:44:14,420
I'm glad you like it.

880
00:44:23,210 --> 00:44:24,130
I have something for you.

881
00:44:24,900 --> 00:44:25,860
What is it?

882
00:44:28,610 --> 00:44:30,820
When you need help, blow this whistle.

883
00:44:31,130 --> 00:44:32,940
My men will come to protect you.

884
00:44:36,090 --> 00:44:37,050
Does that mean

885
00:44:37,570 --> 00:44:38,730
you will always have

886
00:44:38,730 --> 00:44:40,420
someone watching me?

887
00:44:40,900 --> 00:44:42,050
You could see it that way.

888
00:44:43,610 --> 00:44:44,170
Take it.

889
00:44:48,460 --> 00:44:50,730
I just don't want my game
to end prematurely

890
00:44:53,650 --> 00:44:54,610
because

891
00:44:56,130 --> 00:44:57,340
someone else takes my piece.

892
00:44:58,380 --> 00:45:06,300
♪Pushing with fingertips,
hoping time will rewind♪

893
00:45:31,460 --> 00:45:36,940
♪If there are no happy memories♪

894
00:45:39,060 --> 00:45:44,540
♪How can we traverse
the forbidden land of sorrow?♪

895
00:45:46,340 --> 00:45:52,420
♪Two cold and unfeeling bodies♪

896
00:45:53,100 --> 00:46:00,380
♪Holding hands,
can we get through the snow season?♪

897
00:46:01,420 --> 00:46:07,900
♪In the cold wind, in the long night♪

898
00:46:08,700 --> 00:46:14,980
♪Embracing the remaining warmth♪

899
00:46:16,260 --> 00:46:23,500
♪The depth of the sea, unfathomable♪

900
00:46:23,580 --> 00:46:29,580
♪Can it bury yesterday's sighs?♪

901
00:46:30,260 --> 00:46:36,300
♪Continue to love,
cherishing it with my life♪

902
00:46:38,140 --> 00:46:44,860
♪Continue to live,
even with only a glimmer of hope♪

903
00:46:45,980 --> 00:46:52,780
♪Whether in sorrow or joy,
I believe in you♪

904
00:46:53,780 --> 00:46:59,700
♪I'd rather be trapped
in the world's extremes♪

905
00:47:00,420 --> 00:47:07,540
♪Continue to live,
exhausting all courage♪

906
00:47:07,780 --> 00:47:15,060
♪Continue to love,
until the breath runs out♪

907
00:47:15,940 --> 00:47:22,740
♪Traversing half a lifetime
of loneliness, just to meet you♪

908
00:47:23,340 --> 00:47:29,780
♪After the hardships,
never to part again♪

